desiredDepartment.title: road Problems
desiredDepartment.details: The road beside Ranchi high school is totally broken and disrupted due to many large potholes. Kindly fix it as soon as possible
desiredDepartment.analysis: The complaint explicitly mentions 'road problems', 'totally broken and disrupted due to many large potholes', and requests a 'fix'. The image clearly shows a severely damaged road with multiple large potholes. These keywords and visual evidence directly align with the responsibilities of the Municipal Works department under the 'Roads' category. The extent of the damage and the location (beside a high school) suggest a high priority due to potential safety hazards for vehicles and pedestrians.
